text: Evelyn van Leeuwen (born 15 May 1972) is a Dutch wheelchair basketball player. She won a bronze medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2004 Summer Paralympics, 2008 Summer Paralympics, and 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for the Netherlands Category:Dutch wheelchair basketball players
